[
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-2985_153199_000000_000000",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/2985/153199/2985_153199_000000_000000.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-2985",
        "content": "\"I know myself that one cannot help one's sympathies and antipathies,\" thought Prince Andrew, \"so it will not do to present my proposal for the reform of the army regulations to the Emperor personally, but the project will speak for itself.\"",
        "style_prompt": "M_p-normal_s-normal_e-normal",
        "gender": "M",
        "pitch": "normal",
        "speed": "normal",
        "energy": "normal"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-2985_153199_000001_000001",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/2985/153199/2985_153199_000001_000001.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-2985",
        "content": "The field marshal made an appointment to see him, received him graciously, and promised to inform the Emperor.",
        "style_prompt": "M_p-normal_s-normal_e-normal",
        "gender": "M",
        "pitch": "normal",
        "speed": "normal",
        "energy": "normal"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-2985_153199_000001_000002",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/2985/153199/2985_153199_000001_000002.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-2985",
        "content": "A few days later Prince Andrew received notice that he was to go to see the Minister of War, Count Arakcheev.",
        "style_prompt": "M_p-normal_s-normal_e-normal",
        "gender": "M",
        "pitch": "normal",
        "speed": "normal",
        "energy": "normal"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-2985_153199_000004_000000",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/2985/153199/2985_153199_000004_000000.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-2985",
        "content": "\"He is Minister of War, a man trusted by the Emperor, and I need not concern myself about his personal qualities: he has been commissioned to consider my project, so he alone can get it adopted,\" thought Prince Andrew as he waited among a number of important and unimportant people in Count Arakcheev's waiting room.",
        "style_prompt": "M_p-normal_s-fast_e-normal",
        "gender": "M",
        "pitch": "normal",
        "speed": "fast",
        "energy": "normal"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-2985_153199_000005_000001",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/2985/153199/2985_153199_000005_000001.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-2985",
        "content": "Count Arakcheev's anteroom had quite a special character.",
        "style_prompt": "M_p-normal_s-slow_e-low",
        "gender": "M",
        "pitch": "normal",
        "speed": "slow",
        "energy": "low"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-2985_153199_000005_000002",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/2985/153199/2985_153199_000005_000002.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-2985",
        "content": "The faces of the unimportant people awaiting their turn for an audience showed embarrassment and servility; the faces of those of higher rank expressed a common feeling of awkwardness, covered by a mask of unconcern and ridicule of themselves, their situation, and the person for whom they were waiting.",
        "style_prompt": "M_p-normal_s-normal_e-normal",
        "gender": "M",
        "pitch": "normal",
        "speed": "normal",
        "energy": "normal"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-2985_153199_000005_000003",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/2985/153199/2985_153199_000005_000003.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-2985",
        "content": "Some walked thoughtfully up and down, others whispered and laughed.",
        "style_prompt": "M_p-normal_s-normal_e-low",
        "gender": "M",
        "pitch": "normal",
        "speed": "normal",
        "energy": "low"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-2985_153199_000005_000004",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/2985/153199/2985_153199_000005_000004.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-2985",
        "content": "Prince Andrew heard the nickname \"Sila Andreevich\" and the words, \"Uncle will give it to us hot,\" in reference to Count Arakcheev.",
        "style_prompt": "M_p-low_s-normal_e-low",
        "gender": "M",
        "pitch": "low",
        "speed": "normal",
        "energy": "low"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-2985_153200_000020_000001",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/2985/153200/2985_153200_000020_000001.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-2985",
        "content": "His arguments were concise, simple, and clear.",
        "style_prompt": "M_p-low_s-fast_e-normal",
        "gender": "M",
        "pitch": "low",
        "speed": "fast",
        "energy": "normal"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-2985_153200_000022_000000",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/2985/153200/2985_153200_000022_000000.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-2985",
        "content": "\"I do not dispute that, but it cannot be denied that court privileges have attained the same end,\" returned Prince Andrew.",
        "style_prompt": "M_p-normal_s-normal_e-normal",
        "gender": "M",
        "pitch": "normal",
        "speed": "normal",
        "energy": "normal"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-2985_153200_000022_000001",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/2985/153200/2985_153200_000022_000001.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-2985",
        "content": "\"Every courtier considers himself bound to maintain his position worthily.\"",
        "style_prompt": "M_p-high_s-normal_e-low",
        "gender": "M",
        "pitch": "high",
        "speed": "normal",
        "energy": "low"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-2985_153202_000000_000000",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/2985/153202/2985_153202_000000_000000.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-2985",
        "content": "CHAPTER seven",
        "style_prompt": "M_p-low_s-slow_e-low",
        "gender": "M",
        "pitch": "very low",
        "speed": "slow",
        "energy": "very low"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-2985_153202_000001_000002",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/2985/153202/2985_153202_000001_000002.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-2985",
        "content": "He gave money for the erection of temples and supplemented as far as he could the collection of alms, in regard to which the majority of members were stingy and irregular.",
        "style_prompt": "M_p-low_s-fast_e-normal",
        "gender": "M",
        "pitch": "low",
        "speed": "fast",
        "energy": "normal"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-2985_153202_000001_000003",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/2985/153202/2985_153202_000001_000003.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-2985",
        "content": "He supported almost singlehanded a poorhouse the order had founded in Petersburg.",
        "style_prompt": "M_p-normal_s-normal_e-high",
        "gender": "M",
        "pitch": "normal",
        "speed": "normal",
        "energy": "high"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-2985_153202_000002_000000",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/2985/153202/2985_153202_000002_000000.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-2985",
        "content": "His life meanwhile continued as before, with the same infatuations and dissipations.",
        "style_prompt": "M_p-low_s-normal_e-normal",
        "gender": "M",
        "pitch": "low",
        "speed": "normal",
        "energy": "normal"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-2985_153202_000002_000001",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/2985/153202/2985_153202_000002_000001.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-2985",
        "content": "He liked to dine and drink well, and though he considered it immoral and humiliating could not resist the temptations of the bachelor circles in which he moved.",
        "style_prompt": "M_p-low_s-normal_e-low",
        "gender": "M",
        "pitch": "low",
        "speed": "normal",
        "energy": "low"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-2985_153202_000003_000001",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/2985/153202/2985_153202_000003_000001.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-2985",
        "content": "At the same time he felt that the deeper the ground sank under him the closer bound he involuntarily became to the order.",
        "style_prompt": "M_p-normal_s-normal_e-normal",
        "gender": "M",
        "pitch": "normal",
        "speed": "normal",
        "energy": "normal"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-2985_153202_000003_000002",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/2985/153202/2985_153202_000003_000002.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-2985",
        "content": "When he had joined the Freemasons he had experienced the feeling of one who confidently steps onto the smooth surface of a bog.",
        "style_prompt": "M_p-normal_s-normal_e-normal",
        "gender": "M",
        "pitch": "normal",
        "speed": "normal",
        "energy": "normal"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-2985_153202_000003_000003",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/2985/153202/2985_153202_000003_000003.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-2985",
        "content": "When he put his foot down it sank in.",
        "style_prompt": "M_p-low_s-normal_e-normal",
        "gender": "M",
        "pitch": "low",
        "speed": "normal",
        "energy": "normal"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-2985_153202_000004_000000",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/2985/153202/2985_153202_000004_000000.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-2985",
        "content": "Joseph Alexeevich was not in Petersburg-he had of late stood aside from the affairs of the Petersburg lodges, and lived almost entirely in Moscow.",
        "style_prompt": "M_p-low_s-normal_e-normal",
        "gender": "M",
        "pitch": "low",
        "speed": "normal",
        "energy": "normal"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-2985_153202_000005_000000",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/2985/153202/2985_153202_000005_000000.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-2985",
        "content": "He divided the Brothers he knew into four categories.",
        "style_prompt": "M_p-normal_s-fast_e-normal",
        "gender": "M",
        "pitch": "normal",
        "speed": "fast",
        "energy": "normal"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-2985_153202_000005_000003",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/2985/153202/2985_153202_000005_000003.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-2985",
        "content": "His heart was not in the mystical aspect of Freemasonry.",
        "style_prompt": "M_p-low_s-normal_e-low",
        "gender": "M",
        "pitch": "low",
        "speed": "normal",
        "energy": "very low"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-2985_153202_000007_000000",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/2985/153202/2985_153202_000007_000000.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-2985",
        "content": "In the third category he included those Brothers (the majority) who saw nothing in Freemasonry but the external forms and ceremonies, and prized the strict performance of these forms without troubling about their purport or significance.",
        "style_prompt": "M_p-low_s-normal_e-normal",
        "gender": "M",
        "pitch": "low",
        "speed": "normal",
        "energy": "normal"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-2985_153202_000007_000001",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/2985/153202/2985_153202_000007_000001.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-2985",
        "content": "Such were Willarski and even the Grand Master of the principal lodge.",
        "style_prompt": "M_p-low_s-fast_e-high",
        "gender": "M",
        "pitch": "low",
        "speed": "fast",
        "energy": "high"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-2985_153202_000008_000000",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/2985/153202/2985_153202_000008_000000.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-2985",
        "content": "Finally, to the fourth category also a great many Brothers belonged, particularly those who had lately joined.",
        "style_prompt": "M_p-low_s-fast_e-low",
        "gender": "M",
        "pitch": "low",
        "speed": "fast",
        "energy": "low"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-2985_153202_000009_000000",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/2985/153202/2985_153202_000009_000000.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-2985",
        "content": "Pierre began to feel dissatisfied with what he was doing.",
        "style_prompt": "M_p-low_s-normal_e-high",
        "gender": "M",
        "pitch": "low",
        "speed": "normal",
        "energy": "high"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-2985_153202_000009_000001",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/2985/153202/2985_153202_000009_000001.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-2985",
        "content": "Freemasonry, at any rate as he saw it here, sometimes seemed to him based merely on externals.",
        "style_prompt": "M_p-low_s-fast_e-high",
        "gender": "M",
        "pitch": "low",
        "speed": "fast",
        "energy": "high"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-2985_153202_000009_000003",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/2985/153202/2985_153202_000009_000003.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-2985",
        "content": "And so toward the end of the year he went abroad to be initiated into the higher secrets of the order.",
        "style_prompt": "M_p-low_s-normal_e-normal",
        "gender": "M",
        "pitch": "low",
        "speed": "normal",
        "energy": "normal"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-2985_153202_000010_000000",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/2985/153202/2985_153202_000010_000000.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-2985",
        "content": "In the summer of eighteen o nine Pierre returned to Petersburg.",
        "style_prompt": "M_p-low_s-fast_e-high",
        "gender": "M",
        "pitch": "low",
        "speed": "fast",
        "energy": "high"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-2985_153202_000010_000001",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/2985/153202/2985_153202_000010_000001.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-2985",
        "content": "Our Freemasons knew from correspondence with those abroad that Bezukhov had obtained the confidence of many highly placed persons, had been initiated into many mysteries, had been raised to a higher grade, and was bringing back with him much that might conduce to the advantage of the masonic cause in Russia.",
        "style_prompt": "M_p-low_s-fast_e-low",
        "gender": "M",
        "pitch": "low",
        "speed": "fast",
        "energy": "low"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-2985_153202_000010_000002",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/2985/153202/2985_153202_000010_000002.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-2985",
        "content": "The Petersburg Freemasons all came to see him, tried to ingratiate themselves with him, and it seemed to them all that he was preparing something for them and concealing it.",
        "style_prompt": "M_p-low_s-fast_e-low",
        "gender": "M",
        "pitch": "low",
        "speed": "fast",
        "energy": "low"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-2985_153202_000011_000000",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/2985/153202/2985_153202_000011_000000.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-2985",
        "content": "A solemn meeting of the lodge of the second degree was convened, at which Pierre promised to communicate to the Petersburg Brothers what he had to deliver to them from the highest leaders of their order.",
        "style_prompt": "M_p-low_s-fast_e-normal",
        "gender": "M",
        "pitch": "low",
        "speed": "fast",
        "energy": "normal"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-2985_153202_000011_000002",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/2985/153202/2985_153202_000011_000002.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-2985",
        "content": "After the usual ceremonies Pierre rose and began his address.",
        "style_prompt": "M_p-low_s-normal_e-high",
        "gender": "M",
        "pitch": "low",
        "speed": "normal",
        "energy": "high"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-2985_153202_000012_000001",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/2985/153202/2985_153202_000012_000001.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-2985",
        "content": "We are drowsing, but we must act.\" Pierre raised his notebook and began to read.",
        "style_prompt": "M_p-low_s-slow_e-low",
        "gender": "M",
        "pitch": "low",
        "speed": "slow",
        "energy": "low"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-2985_153202_000014_000001",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/2985/153202/2985_153202_000014_000001.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-2985",
        "content": "But in these great endeavors we are gravely hampered by the political institutions of today.",
        "style_prompt": "M_p-normal_s-fast_e-normal",
        "gender": "M",
        "pitch": "normal",
        "speed": "fast",
        "energy": "normal"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-2985_153202_000014_000002",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/2985/153202/2985_153202_000014_000002.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-2985",
        "content": "What is to be done in these circumstances?",
        "style_prompt": "M_p-normal_s-fast_e-normal",
        "gender": "M",
        "pitch": "normal",
        "speed": "fast",
        "energy": "normal"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-2985_153202_000014_000003",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/2985/153202/2985_153202_000014_000003.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-2985",
        "content": "To favor revolutions, overthrow everything, repel force by force?...",
        "style_prompt": "M_p-normal_s-fast_e-high",
        "gender": "M",
        "pitch": "normal",
        "speed": "fast",
        "energy": "high"
    },
    {
